sections.content:
{{date current_date "MMMM DD, YYYY"}}

VIA {{#if friendly}}REGULAR MAIL{{else}}CERTIFIED MAIL, RETURN RECEIPT REQUESTED{{/if}}

{{recipient_name}}
{{recipient_address}}

Re: {{#if patent}}Patent{{/if}}{{#if trademark}}Trademark{{/if}}{{#if copyright}}Copyright{{/if}}{{#if trade_secret}}Trade Secret{{/if}} Infringement - Cease and Desist Demand

{{#if patent}}Your unauthorized use of our patented technology constitutes patent infringement under 35 U.S.C. ยง 271. Patent infringement carries significant penalties, including injunctive relief and damages.{{/if}}

{{#if trademark}}Your use of a confusingly similar mark constitutes trademark infringement under 15 U.S.C. ยง 1114 and unfair competition under 15 U.S.C. ยง 1125(a). This creates a likelihood of confusion among consumers.{{/if}}

{{#if copyright}}Your unauthorized copying and use of our copyrighted work constitutes copyright infringement under 17 U.S.C. ยง 501. Copyright infringement can result in statutory damages up to $150,000 per work for willful infringement.{{/if}}

{{#if trade_secret}}Your unauthorized use of our confidential and proprietary information constitutes misappropriation of trade secrets under [applicable state law/DTSA]. This breach of confidentiality has caused substantial harm to our business.{{/if}}

Therefore, we demand that you:

{{#if stop_use}}1. IMMEDIATELY CEASE AND DESIST from all use of our {{#if patent}}patented technology{{/if}}{{#if trademark}}trademark{{/if}}{{#if copyright}}copyrighted work{{/if}}{{#if trade_secret}}trade secrets{{/if}};
{{/if}}
{{#if destroy_inventory}}2. DESTROY all inventory, marketing materials, and other items that infringe our intellectual property;
{{/if}}
{{#if accounting}}3. PROVIDE a full accounting of all sales and profits derived from your infringing activities;
{{/if}}
{{#if licensing_discussion}}4. CONTACT US to discuss a possible licensing arrangement if you wish to continue using our intellectual property;
{{/if}}
5. CONFIRM IN WRITING within {{response_deadline}} days that you have complied with these demands.

{{#if friendly}}We hope to resolve this matter amicably and avoid the need for legal action. However, if necessary, we are prepared to protect our intellectual property rights through appropriate legal channels.{{/if}}

{{#if professional}}If you fail to comply with these demands, we will have no choice but to consider all available legal remedies, including filing a lawsuit seeking injunctive relief, damages, and attorneys' fees.{{/if}}

{{#if firm}}Failure to comply with these demands will leave us no alternative but to pursue all available legal remedies, including immediate legal action for injunctive relief, damages, profits, and attorneys' fees.{{/if}}

{{#if aggressive}}Be advised that continued infringement after receipt of this notice constitutes willful infringement, which may result in enhanced damages and attorneys' fees. We are prepared to immediately file suit to protect our client's rights.{{/if}}

{{#if friendly}}We trust that this matter can be resolved quickly and amicably. Please contact us at your earliest convenience to discuss this matter.{{/if}}

{{#if professional}}We await your prompt response and compliance with these demands.{{/if}}

{{#if firm}}This is a serious matter requiring your immediate attention. Govern yourself accordingly.{{/if}}

{{#if aggressive}}Time is of the essence. This letter is written without prejudice to any other rights or remedies available to our client, all of which are expressly reserved.{{/if}}

You must respond within {{response_deadline}} days of the date of this letter.

Sincerely,

[ATTORNEY NAME]
[FIRM NAME]
[PHONE]
[EMAIL]

Attorney for {{sender_name}}
